	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001206_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'--> 
<!--Hand 01 68566 top left--><!--Hand 02 25 top left-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>18 Hart <choice><abbr>St.</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Bloomsbury <choice><abbr>Sq</abbr><expan>Square</expan></choice></placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">6<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi><choice><abbr>Feb<hi rend="sup">y</hi></abbr><expan>February</expan></choice></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1858</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>Sir</persName></p>
<lb/><p>the only day 
<lb/>I have next week 
<lb/>is Tuesday, and 
<lb/>that in consequence 
<lb/>of the authorities 
<lb/>having refused 
<lb/><persName>my brother in law</persName>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001206_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'--> 
<lb/>permission to go 
<lb/>to Africa. He 
<lb/>was about to 
<lb/>marry on that 
<lb/>day and a change 
<lb/>of wind having 
<lb/>taken place at 
<lb/>the mission house 
<lb/>he is requested 
<lb/>to study medicine 
<lb/>for two months! 
<lb/>I was sorry that 
<lb/>I could not fulfil 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001206_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'--> 
<lb/>my intention of 
<lb/>visiting you before 
<lb/>but now the 
<lb/>time is past, as 
<lb/>next week is our 
<lb/>last. Next Monday 
<lb/>week we go to 
<lb/>see our children 
<lb/>and do not return 
<lb/>to London again 
<lb/>as we sail a 
<lb/>few days after</p>
<lb/><p>Thanks for your 
<lb/>kind thought<del type="strikethrough">s</del> about 
<lb/>me. I regret 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001206_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'--> 
<lb/>that pressing duties 
<lb/>have prevented my 
<lb/>seeing you more</p>
<lb/><p>I have not seen 
<lb/><persName>Rookes'</persName> letters 
<lb/>unless his were 
<lb/>among a host 
<lb/>which have 
<lb/>been sent to me 
<lb/>&amp; which I could 
<lb/>not even look 
<lb/>at</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Yours very truly</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p><persName><choice><abbr>Rev<hi rend="sup">d</hi></abbr><expan>Reverend</expan></choice> H. Allon</persName></p>
			
</div>
